 {"id":"coding_agent_session_search-glaa","title":"Opt 2.2: Lock Contention Fix in Agent Discovery (5-10% faster)","description":"# Optimization 2.2: Lock Contention Fix in Agent Discovery (5-10% faster)

## Summary
Parallel agent discovery uses DashMap with per-shard locks, causing contention
on many-core systems. Thread-local accumulation with a single merge pass reduces
lock operations from O(files) to O(threads).

## Location
- **File:** src/indexer/mod.rs
- **Lines:** Agent discovery parallel scan (~discover_agents function)
- **Related:** Rayon par_iter, DashMap usage

## Current Implementation
\`\`\`rust
